Get GALA

There are many ways to get and use GALA within the Gala Games ecosystem. The central focus of Gala Games is…well…GAMES. However, we do know that people want to know how to get GALA to use in-game and to purchase items.

How to Get GALA

Gala Coin

  • First, Gala Coin purchased through the Gala operating platform, by purchasing the license to operate the Gala node, you will get the opportunity to get rewarded for your contribution to the network, and the tight control of assets and game accounts has stifled a lot of creative thinking.
  • Second, decentralized Gala Games ecosystem is eager to open the doors to players regaining the control they deserve, and if you win a magical sword in a game on the Gala gaming platform, it's yours.
  • third, It is a verifiable asset on the blockchain, you can trade with others or players in the game, we do not have the right to take the sword from your hands, we can not prevent another company from making a game that uses the sword at the same time, we want to encourage the possibilities in this field.
  • fourth, The decentralized Gala Games ecosystem wants players not only to own their own in-game items, but also to have a say in the evolution of the Gala Games roadmap, with players and node owners involved through a distributed voting mechanism to help determine which games should be added to the platform or which should be funded by the decentralized Gala Games ecosystem.
  • Fifth, therefore, the launch of the Gala coin holding feedback agent registration, by the Gala operation to recruit the external coin holding agents, so as to promote the growth of the Gala Games mechanism and price stability, but also to avoid a large number of sales of Gala Coin holders, to avoid causing the price of Gala to fall.
  • sixth, In addition to purchasing games within the platform and obtaining node licenses from official operators, holders of Gala can also obtain the qualification permissions and feedback of agents by holding Gala tokens.
  • Seventh,The proportion of rewards for each issuance is, the owner of the coin: 50%, the agent: 50% After 7 days of holding by the coin holder and the agent, and on the first Friday, the distribution reward is issued to the holder of the coin 12.5%/Gala Coin, and the distribution reward is issued to the agent 12.5%/Gala Coin.
